你能够调用以下的API:
[['PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', {'name': 'PolygonFinance.get_ticker_news', 'description': 'get the most recent news articles relating to a stock ticker symbol', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [{'name': 'ticker', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'Return results that contain this ticker'}], 'return_data': [{'name': 'results', 'description': 'A list of news including title, summary, and author'}]}], ['ForeignExchangeAPI.get_currency_exchange_rate', {'name': 'ForeignExchangeAPI.get_currency_exchange_rate', 'description': 'Get the exchange rate of a currency pair over a specified period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'currencyPair', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The currency pair in the format of CUR1CUR2.'}, {'name': 'period', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The period over which to retrieve the exchange rate data, e.g., 7d, 1m, 1y.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'rateData', 'description': 'A list of exchange rates over the specified period.'}]}], ['StockMarketAPI.get_index_data', {'name': 'StockMarketAPI.get_index_data', 'description': 'Get the real-time data of a specified stock market index.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'index', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock market index symbol.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'indexData', 'description': 'The real-time data of the specified index including current value, change, and percentage change.'}]}], ['EconomicNewsAPI.get_policy_news', {'name': 'EconomicNewsAPI.get_policy_news', 'description': 'Get the latest news related to economic policies of a specified country.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'country', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The country for which to retrieve policy news.'}, {'name': 'topic', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The specific topic of the policy news, e.g., central bank policy, fiscal policy.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'newsArticles', 'description': 'A list of news articles related to the specified policy topic.'}]}], ['InvestmentAdviceAPI.get_investment_advice', {'name': 'InvestmentAdviceAPI.get_investment_advice', 'description': 'Get investment advice based on recent policy changes and market volatility.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'index', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The stock market index for which to provide advice.'}, {'name': 'policyChanges', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The nature of recent policy changes, e.g., latest, significant.'}, {'name': 'marketVolatility', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The level of market volatility, e.g., low, medium, high.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'advice', 'description': 'Investment advice based on the specified parameters.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
